         <abstract>
            <p>We consider (n, m) Chebyshev formulae of algebraic degree m using n nodes. The aim of this short note is to show that by a simple algebraic method C. Posse's theorem concerning Gaussian quadrature of Chebyshev type can be improved. Furthermore, we given an application of this method to Gauss-Kronrod quadrature of Chebyshev type.</p>
          </abstract>
